<h1>Pricing</h1>
<p>progrok proxies xAI's API — these are the upstream costs (free through OAuth).</p>

<h2>Text Models</h2>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Model</th><th>Input</th><th>Output</th><th>Cached</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>grok-4.3</td><td>$1.25 / 1M</td><td>$2.50 / 1M</td><td>$0.31 / 1M</td></tr>
<tr><td>grok-build-0.1</td><td>$1.00 / 1M</td><td>$2.00 / 1M</td><td>$0.25 / 1M</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h2>Imagine API</h2>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Type</th><th>Price</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Image (standard)</td><td>$0.02 / image</td></tr>
<tr><td>Image (quality)</td><td>$0.04 / image</td></tr>
<tr><td>Video</td><td>$0.05 / sec</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h2>Voice API</h2>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Service</th><th>Price</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Text to Speech</td><td>$0.01 / 1K chars</td></tr>
<tr><td>Speech to Text</td><td>$0.003 / min</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</main>
<footer style="margin-top:3rem;padding-top:1rem;border-top:1px solid #30363d;color:#8b949e;font-size:.85em">progrok — MIT License</footer>
